Showa Aluminium Corp is issuing a 100 mlndlr equity warrant eurobond due April 23, 1992 paying anindicated coupon of 2-1/8 pct and priced at par, lead managerNomura International Ltd said.    Final terms will be fixed on April 15. The sellingconcession is 1-1/2 pct while management and underwritingcombined pays 3/4 pct. The non-callable bond is available indenominations of 5,000 dlrs and will be listed in Luxembourg.    The payment date is April 23. REUTER&#3;